the lion of bourdillon is a 2015 documentary film aired by africa independent television , a nigerian television station popularly known as ait .   the film centers on the political life of senator bola tinubu , the former lagos state governor and the national leader of the all progressives congress .   it was first aired on march 1 , 2015 , but then stopped from further airing on march 6 , 2015 following a n150 billion libel suit filled by tinubu against ait .